reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easier and better than buying from a bedding store
reviews.reviewText: The frame broke on one of our beds right before Christmas and I didn’t have time to store shop for another.I also didn’t think I could find a store that could deliver overnight - so my husband won’t have to sleep on the couch for too many days. I decided to check out bed frames on Amazon.Boy! I’m glad I did. I found this bedframe that was inexpensive and the right size. Best of all it was delivered within 24 hours, it was easy to assemble, study and easy to move. My husband says he feels comfortable knowing that the frame feels sturdy, does not wobble or squeak.Nothing fancy, just a good solid bedframe at a great price.I made a great choice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This frame arrived quickly in a surprisingly compact cardboard box. Simple assembly to put together following instructions, support our mattress and fits perfectly. We have not used it a lot, but after some initial test, it seems very sturdy and does not make annoying squeaking noises. It also has comfortable height off the ground with plenty space under bed for storage we need. Reasonably priced compared with other products, but its quality seems very good as well.
